    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, but all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brakes or tires.",
      "price": 19500.0,
